---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
---

<MainLayout title="David Hoang">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Designer + Investor</h1>
      <p>I'm building and investing in tools that revolutionize the internet. Currently I am VP&nbsp;of&nbsp;Design,&nbsp;AI at <a href="https://atlassian.com" target="_blank">Atlassian</a> and Advisor for <a href="https://play.com" target="_blank">Play</a>.</p>
      <p>Quick links:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Subscribe to my newsletter, <a href="https://www.proofofconcept.pub" target="_blank">Proof of Concept</a></li>
        <li>Buy the zine, <a href="https://davidhoang.gumroad.com/l/proof-of-concept-000-series">Proof of Concept: The 000 Series</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/davidhoang">Follow me on GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://youtu.be/piGC-iFwmrk?si=RuQtmVtimws3npVM">Watch my talk from Config 2021</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Z88rLjF-lc">Listen to my interview on Dive Club</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <div class="theme-image" aria-label="Photo of David"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="design-philosophy">
    <h2>Design philosophy</h2>
    
    <div class="philosophy-grid">
      <div class="philosophy-item">
        <p><strong>Seek paradigm shifts.</strong> Imagine the future and build it now. Those who can spot trends of shifts will have enduring success.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="philosophy-item" id="e3d275">
        <p><strong>Embrace the entrepreneurial spirit</strong>Act like the owner of everything you do.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="philosophy-item">
        <p><strong>Software is beautiful</strong>It's not just about the code. It's about the experience.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="philosophy-item" id="647f3a">
        <p><strong>Method makes magic.</strong> Design is not magic. It's a methodâ€”a rigorous process of exploration, iteration, and validation until you reach your outcome that feels like magic.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="philosophy-item">
        <p><strong>Iteration over perfectionism</strong> The number one way to be more productive is to reduce the iteration cycle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
